データの可視化¶
















量的変数と質的変数を分ける関数を作成¶












In [9]:



    


def numlist(df):
    numberlist = []
    d = dict(df.dtypes)
    for i in d.keys():
        if d[i] != 'object':
            numberlist.append(i)
    df_num = df.loc[:,numberlist]
    return(df_num.head())


def objlist(df):
    objectlist = []
    d = dict(df.dtypes)
    for i in d.keys():
        if d[i] == 'object':
            objectlist.append(i)
    df_num = df.loc[:,objectlist]
    return(df_num.head())





















欠損値があっても相関係数を算出する関数を作成¶












In [15]:



    


## 
import scipy as sp
# x,y df[???],df[???]
def corr_nun(x,y):
    # x,y
    train_1_corr1=pd.concat([x,y],axis=1)
    # 
    train_1_corr2=train_1_corr1.dropna()
    # 
    corr=sp.stats.pearsonr(train_1_corr2.iloc[:,0],train_1_corr2.iloc[:,1])
    return(corr[0])

# 'SalePrice'
train_1_objlist=objlist(train_1)
